1. *Upropastio* si ceo dan svojim negativnim stavom. (You ruined your entire day with your negative attitude.)
2. Da li ćeš *upropastiti* večeras svojim neumerenim pijanstvom? (Will you ruin tonight with your excessive drinking?)
3. Ona je odlučila da neće dozvoliti da je ljubav *upropasti*. (She decided not to let love ruin her.)
4. Nažalost, loša vremenska prognoza je *upropastila* naš plan za piknik. (Unfortunately, the bad weather forecast ruined our picnic plan.)
5. Niko neće verovati da si ti *upropastio* ovaj projekat tako lošim planom. (No one will believe that you ruined this project with such a bad plan.)
6. Svojom neopreznosti, vozač je *upropastio* automobil i ozbiljno se povredio. (With his carelessness, the driver ruined the car and seriously injured himself.)
7. Da li ćeš me *upropastiti* kod šefa ako ispričaš sve što si čuo? (Will you ruin me with the boss if you tell him everything you heard?)
8. Naša vlast je *upropastila* zdravstveni sistem zemlje. (Our government has ruined the country's healthcare system.)
9. *Upropastila* sam kolače koji su bili prepečeni i tvrdi. (I ruined the cakes that were overcooked and hard.)
10. Ne želim da *upropastim* naše prijateljstvo zbog nečega što je moglo biti rešeno razgovorom. (I don't want to ruin our friendship over something that could have been resolved through conversation.)